        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>Vehicles equipped with International T 444E, DT 466E and 530E engines and Allison AT or MT
                    transmissions may experience harsh (abrupt) 1-2 or 2-3 upshifts. Kit part number 2500739C91,
                    containing a switch and installation hardware, is available to eliminate harsh (abrupt) upshift
                    complaints. The switch is wired into the transmission modulator control relay and activated by the
                    throttle pedal resulting in a faster ON signal to the transmission modulator control relay.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
